   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>NN, strategos of the leontopolite nome through NN basilikos grammateus acting as strategos to NN, strategos of Bousirites my loving friend, greetings. ... and before I have declared to ... and now, my brother I am writing that the fields in the Leontopolites never were inundated. You can see that ... you inspect ...</ab>
         </div>
